episodes.title: The 'Exclusive Brethren': Church Or Cult?
episodes.description:
A Perth man's revealed the heartache of seeing his family torn apart by what he believes is an extremist cult. Matt Cook was raised in the "Exclusive Brethren" and was forced to leave because he was gay... he's bravely shared his story with 10 News First.
